<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12453] Make region available once it&apos;s open</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12453</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently (in trunk, with zk-less assignment), a region is available to serving requests only after RS notifies the master the region is open, and the meta is updated with the new location. We may be able to do better than this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
